-- Crear la tabla en SQL Data Warehouse

CREATE TABLE business_google (
    address VARCHAR(100),
    avg_rating FLOAT,
    gmap_id VARCHAR(100),
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT,
    name VARCHAR(100),
    count_reviews BIGINT,
    url VARCHAR(100),
    category VARCHAR(100),
    state VARCHAR(100)
);
